documents: The Gates of Morning is written by Henry De Vere Stacpoole . The novel is based on a novel by Henry De Vère Stacpolle, a book by Robert Leighton-Smith . Review the following summary for clarity, grammar, and conciseness .

The Gates of Morning is published by Henry De Vere Stacpoole, Georgina Staplia, and is published in Book 1; Stellia; Scrutopia in Spanish, French and Spanish; Philippines; Europeans; Portugal; Argentina; .

The Gates of Morning is published by Henry De Vere Stacpoole . In the book, a strange new figure was sent by the gods to the island of Karolin . It is the tale of a strange stranger sent from the island, an island beautiful as a dream, yet swarming with devils .
